{"tid":1188932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"單車巡遊抗惡法","createTime":"2019-06-06T14:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T15:11:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c9019de0e117c3fad943b5fef3e0e6a9fce4940","tid":1188932,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T14:33:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190606/20697054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F20697054&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=02de55e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F20697054&h=b9d16a1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190606/20697054</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n單車巡遊抗惡法<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190606/large/a0605a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190606%2Flarge%2Fa0605a.gif&h=054b6da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】為抵抗送中惡法，南區區議員司馬文聯同被港府DQ的立法會前議員姚松炎和單車愛好者（圖），於明日以單車巡遊港島，亦計劃在九龍巡遊，呼籲市民周日上街。姚表示，預料有50人的單車隊伍，明日下午3時在北角碼頭集合出發，然後驅往金鐘政總，路程全長約5公里，其間途經人流密集之處，會廣播呼籲市民周日上街。他指港府硬推《逃犯條例》修訂，把香港一國兩制摧毀成一國一制，失去原有的自由和人權，同時導致國際資金流走，市民必須一同力抗惡法。<br />\n<br />\n謝榮耀攝   <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：法律界今黑衣遊行 郭榮鏗：娥特衰過689<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n文子星：因支持錫克人獨立被政治檢控<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n中大關注組派單張力陳禍害<br />\n<br />\n法律界今黑衣遊行 郭榮鏗：娥特衰過689<br />\n民陣冀100萬人上街嚇退林鄭<br />\n唔想等死 連登仔沉默中爆發巴絲打夾錢製傳單 團結年輕人上街<br />\n潮店6.9休市：總有事比賺錢重要<br />\n高登巴打改歌 望人留戀香港<br />\nEndgame令分裂變槍口對外<br />\n惡法睇真啲：無公平審訊是最根本問題<br />\n李家超避談中國人權差劣死撐「歐美不會因他國法治排名低而拒移交」<br />\n民主派狙擊送中局長 范國威受傷<br />\n港府去信立會反對泛民56修正案<br />\n彭定康拍片斥堵漏洞論「虛假惹人發笑」指港府修例危害國際地位<br />\n林鄭晤70國領事解釋修例<br />\n千六警部署反送中遊行 水炮車不出動<br />\n文子星：因支持錫克人獨立被政治檢控<br />\n中大關注組派單張力陳禍害<br />\n罕有強硬聲明「特首非普選 送中無保障」律師會促擱置惡法"},{"pid":"ffadabf1486eedb611050ecd7725d0b27d55dcab","tid":1188932,"uid":8605,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T14:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我有時真係好佩服佢地諗到咁多呢d無謂野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遲下可以一班麻甩佬去禁鐘仔 叫雞抗惡法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jsZwe8f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjsZwe8f.png&h=c40108e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"974f996a1f7d03072eb7ce2f957220d912ca6a59","tid":1188932,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:03:35.000Z","msg":"踩單車都得&hellip;咁6月10號咪即係全民返工抗惡法"},{"pid":"3925f4f7d7372915bf50be36a1e7ddbbd6b46153","tid":1188932,"uid":50719,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"起碼比批鬥達哥更有影響力(?)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acad2e491750fa156f494132630f0c9bb7377be","tid":1188932,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c709fb71cbfde0cf37a7a3a9bb07b636d9bab98a","tid":1188932,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:11:09.000Z","msg":"on 999"}]}